script.name: plugin.advjump.menu.event
script.sourceplaintext:
$pageid = get global variable: name='advjump.pageid' $cmd.id = 226 $ship.sector = $a.obj -> get sector $player.sector = [PLAYERSHIP] -> get sector $ship = $a.obj $advjump = $a.obj -> get amount of ware Advanced Jumpdrive in cargo bay $advtarget = $a.obj -> get amount of ware FTL Jumpdrive Extension in cargo bay $energy.gen = $a.obj -> get amount of ware Jumpdrive Energy Generator in cargo bay
if not $a.obj -> is of class Ship $isWing = [TRUE] end
if $a.event == [MEvent.CmdCheck] if not $a.obj -> get amount of ware Navigation Command Software MK1 in cargo bay return [CmdConCheck.Disabled] end if not $a.obj -> get amount of ware Advanced Jumpdrive in cargo bay if not $a.obj -> get amount of ware Jumpdrive in cargo bay return [CmdConCheck.Disabled] end end return [CmdConCheck.Available]
else if $a.event == 'run' set global variable: name='advjump.run' value=[TRUE]
else if $a.event == [MEvent.Returned] $menu.id = $a.value[0] $selection = $a.value[1] $value = $a.value[2] if $menu.id == 'advjump.menu' if $selection == 'target' if not is datatype[ $value ] == DATATYPE_NULL if $value -> exists $input = create menu return to previous menu: value=$value return $input else if is datatype[ $value ] == DATATYPE_ARRAY $input = create menu return to previous menu: value=$value return $input end end else if $selection == 'advjump.mystation' if $value -> exists $input = create menu return to previous menu: value=$value return $input end else if $selection == 'advjump.gateless' if $value -> exists $input = create menu return to previous menu: value=$value return $input end else if $selection == 'advjump.beacons' if $value -> exists $input = create menu return to previous menu: value=$value return $input end end end
else if $a.event == [MEvent.Start] gosub sub.BuildMenu return $input
else if $a.event == 'advjump.menu' if is datatype[ $a.value ] == DATATYPE_ARRAY $size = size of array $a.value skip if $size == 4 $a.value = $a.value[0] end if $a.value -> exists set global variable: name='advjump.menu.target' value=$a.value return [TRUE] else if is datatype[ $a.value ] == DATATYPE_ARRAY set global variable: name='advjump.menu.target' value=$a.value return [TRUE] end
else if $a.event == 'sector' $text = read text: page=$pageid id=11 if $advjump $input = create input: id='target', user input=Var/Sector, refobj=$a.obj, description=$text, without sector=[FALSE], filterclass=null, racemask=null, flags=null, default=$ship.sector else $input = create input: id='target', user input=Var/Sector for Jumpdrive, refobj=$a.obj, description=$text, without sector=[FALSE], filterclass=null, racemask=null, flags=null, default=$ship.sector end return $input
else if $a.event == 'gate' $text = read text: page=$pageid id=13 if $advjump $input = create input: id='target', user input=Var/Warpgate, refobj=$a.obj, description=$text, without sector=[FALSE], filterclass=null, racemask=null, flags=null, default=$ship.sector else $input = create input: id='target', user input=Var/Jumpdrive Gate, refobj=$a.obj, description=$text, without sector=[FALSE], filterclass=null, racemask=null, flags=null, default=$ship.sector end return $input
else if $a.event == 'station' $text = read text: page=$pageid id=14 $input = create input: id='target', user input=Var/Station/Carrier to dock at, refobj=$a.obj, description=$text, without sector=[FALSE], filterclass=null, racemask=null, flags=null, default=$ship.sector return $input
else if $a.event == 'pos' $text = read text: page=$pageid id=16 $input = create input: id='target', user input=Var/Sector Position, refobj=$a.obj, description=$text, without sector=[FALSE], filterclass=null, racemask=null, flags=null, default=$ship.sector return $input
else if $a.event == 'ftl' $text = read text: page=$pageid id=19 $input = create input: id='target', user input=Var/Sector Position, refobj=$ship.sector, description=$text, without sector=[TRUE], filterclass=null, racemask=null, flags=null, default=$ship.sector return $input
else if $a.event == 'mystation' $text = read text: page=$pageid id=15 $search.string = get global variable: name='advjump.menu.search' @ $menu = [THIS] -> call script lib.cycrow.menu.mystations : Ignore Array=null Race=Player Class Filter=Station Title=$text Return Menu?=[TRUE] Search String=null if $menu set menu option: $menu, allow searching=[TRUE] $input = create input: id='advjump.mystation' menu=$menu title=$text description=$a.obj callback=null return $input end
else if $a.event == 'gateless' gosub sub.Gateless return $input
else if $a.event == 'beacon' @ $input = [THIS] -> call script plugin.advjump.getbeacon : Search String=null $input = $input[1] return $input
else if $a.event == [MEvent.Search] $menu.id = $a.value[0] $search.string = $a.value[1] set global variable: name='advjump.menu.search' value=$search.string if $menu.id == 'advjump.mystation' $text = read text: page=$pageid id=15 @ $menu = [THIS] -> call script lib.cycrow.menu.mystations : Ignore Array=null Race=Player Class Filter=Station Title=$text Return Menu?=[TRUE] Search String=$search.string if $menu set menu option: $menu, allow searching=[TRUE] return $menu end else if $menu.id == 'advjump.beacons' @ $input = [THIS] -> call script plugin.advjump.getbeacon : Search String=$search.string $menu = $input[0] return $menu end
else if $a.event == [MEvent.Arguments] $target = get global variable: name='advjump.menu.target' $ret = create new array, arguments=$target, null, null, null, null return $ret
else if $a.event == [MEvent.Finished] if get global variable: name='advjump.run' $target = get global variable: name='advjump.menu.target' @ START $a.obj -> call script plugin.advjump.cmd.jump : Jump Target=$target end set global variable: name='advjump.run' value=null set global variable: name='advjump.menu.target' value=null set global variable: name='advjump.menu.search' value=null end
return null
sub.BuildMenu: $menu = create custom menu array
if ! $advjump $text = read text: page=$pageid id=3 else $text = read text: page=$pageid id=2 end add custom menu heading to array $menu: title=$text
$text = read text: page=$pageid id=4 add custom menu item to array $menu: text=$text nextinput='sector' value=null $text = read text: page=$pageid id=12 add custom menu item to array $menu: text=$text nextinput='gate' value=null $text = read text: page=$pageid id=5 add custom menu item to array $menu: text=$text nextinput='station' value=null
@ if [THIS] -> call script plugin.advjump.getsectors : $text = read text: page=$pageid id=24 add custom menu item to array $menu: text=$text nextinput='gateless' value=null end
$aStations = get station array: of race Player class/type=Station if $aStations if size of array $aStations $text = read text: page=$pageid id=15 add custom menu item to array $menu: text=$text nextinput='mystation' value=null end end
if $ship.sector != $player.sector $text = read text: page=$pageid id=6 add custom menu item to array $menu: text=$text returnvalue=[PLAYERSHIP] end
$text = read text: page=$pageid id=7 add custom menu item to array $menu: text=$text nextinput='pos' value=null
@ $aBeacons = [THIS] -> call script lib.cycrow.findbeacons : if $aBeacons if size of array $aBeacons $text = read text: page=$pageid id=30 add custom menu item to array $menu: text=$text nextinput='beacon' value=null end end
if $advjump AND $advtarget $text = read text: page=$pageid id=26 add custom menu item to array $menu: text=$text nextinput='ftl' value=null end
$lastPos = get global variable: name='advjump.lastpos' $lastObj = get global variable: name='advjump.lastobj' $lastSector = get global variable: name='advjump.lastsector' if ! $advjump $text = read text: page=$pageid id=9 else $text = read text: page=$pageid id=8 end add custom menu heading to array $menu: title=$text
* Nearest Shipyard $flags = [Find.Nearest] | [Find.Known] | [Find.DockingAllowed] $shipyard = find station in galaxy: startsector=$ship.sector class or type=Shipyard race=null flags=$flags refobj=$a.obj serial=null max.jumps=100 if $shipyard -> exists $sSector = $shipyard -> get sector $text = sprintf: pageid=$pageid textid=28, $sSector, null, null, null, null add custom menu item to array $menu: text=$text returnvalue=$shipyard end
* Nearest Equipment Dock $eq = find station in galaxy: startsector=$ship.sector class or type=Equipment Dock race=null flags=$flags refobj=$a.obj serial=null max.jumps=100 if $eq -> exists $sSector = $eq -> get sector $text = sprintf: pageid=$pageid textid=29, $sSector, null, null, null, null add custom menu item to array $menu: text=$text returnvalue=$eq end
$eq = find station in galaxy: startsector=$ship.sector class or type=Trading Dock race=null flags=$flags refobj=$a.obj serial=null max.jumps=100 if $eq -> exists $sSector = $eq -> get sector $text = sprintf: pageid=$pageid textid=34, $sSector, null, null, null, null add custom menu item to array $menu: text=$text returnvalue=$eq end
$eq = find station in galaxy: startsector=$ship.sector class or type=Dock race=Pirates flags=$flags refobj=$a.obj serial=null max.jumps=100 if $eq -> exists $sSector = $eq -> get sector $text = sprintf: pageid=$pageid textid=36, $sSector, null, null, null, null add custom menu item to array $menu: text=$text returnvalue=$eq end
if ! $advjump @ $eq = $ship -> call script lib.cycrow.findnearestproduct : Product=Energy Cells if $eq -> exists $text = sprintf: pageid=$pageid textid=35, $eq, null, null, null, null add custom menu item to array $menu: text=$text returnvalue=$eq end end
if $lastSector $text = sprintf: pageid=$pageid textid=17, $lastSector, null, null, null, null add custom menu item to array $menu: text=$text returnvalue=$lastSector end if $lastObj $text = sprintf: pageid=$pageid textid=10, $lastObj, null, null, null, null add custom menu item to array $menu: text=$text returnvalue=$lastObj end if $lastPos $sector = $lastPos[3] $x = $lastPos[0] $y = $lastPos[1] $z = $lastPos[2] $text = sprintf: fmt='%s (%s, %s, %s)', $sector, $x, $y, $z, null $text = sprintf: pageid=$pageid textid=18, $text, null, null, null, null add custom menu item to array $menu: text=$text returnvalue=$lastPos end
$text = read text: page=2022 id=$cmd.id add custom menu info line to array $menu: text=$text add custom menu info line to array $menu: text=' ' if $advjump OR $energy.gen $text = read text: page=$pageid id=22 $text = sprintf: pageid=$pageid textid=21, $text, $text, null, null, null else $ship.sector = $ship -> get sector $needed = $ship -> needed jump drive energy for jump to sector $ship.sector $got = $ship -> get true amount of ware Energy Cells in cargo bay $jumps = $got / $needed skip if $jumps $jumps = 0 $text = sprintf: pageid=$pageid textid=21, $got, $jumps, null, null, null end add custom menu info line to array $menu: text=$text
if $advtarget $text = read text: page=$pageid id=23 add custom menu info line to array $menu: text=$text end
if $isWing $text = sprintf: pageid=$pageid textid=33, $ship, null, null, null, null add custom menu info line to array $menu: text=$text $aWingShips = get flight wing ship array: wing=$ship $c = size of array $aWingShips while $c dec $c = $wing.ship = $aWingShips[$c] if $wing.ship -> get true amount of ware Advanced Jumpdrive in cargo bay $text = create new array, arguments=20, $wing.ship, -1, Advanced Jumpdrive, null add custom menu info line to array $menu: text=$text else if $wing.ship -> get true amount of ware Jumpdrive in cargo bay $text = create new array, arguments=20, $wing.ship, -1, Jumpdrive, null add custom menu info line to array $menu: text=$text end end end
set menu option: $menu, icon=30
$title = read text: page=2010 id=$cmd.id $text = $a.obj -> get name $input = create input: id='advjump.menu' menu=$menu title=$title description=$text callback=null endsub
sub.Gateless: @ $tSectors = [THIS] -> call script plugin.advjump.getsectors : $menu = create custom menu array
$aSectors = sort table keys: table=$tSectors $size = size of array $aSectors $i = 0 $added = [FALSE] while $i < $size $sector = $aSectors[$i] inc $i = $text = $sector -> get name if $search.string skip if case insensitive string match, is $search.string in $text continue end $text.cols = array alloc: size=2 $text = create custom menu column string, position=0 length=250 right=[FALSE] colour=null text=$sector $text.cols[0] = $text $sector.owner = $sector -> get owner race $text = create custom menu column string, position=-1 length=100 right=[TRUE] colour=null text=$sector.owner $text.cols[1] = $text add custom menu item to array $menu: text=$text.cols returnvalue=$sector $added = [TRUE] end
if not $added $text = read text: page=[Page.Menus] id=711 add non selectable menu item: $menu, text=$text end
set menu option: $menu, icon=51 set menu option: $menu, allow searching=[TRUE]
$title = read text: page=$pageid id=24 $text = $a.obj -> get name $input = create input: id='advjump.gateless' menu=$menu title=$title description=$text callback=null endsub
return null
